{
  "stem": "27390.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We would run-- we didn't know where we were running, away-- away from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Germans were coming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we run like this till we came on the-- on-- outside the city, the suburbs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the planes came down, the German planes came down and they started shooting into the crowds with machine guns.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They could see-- they came very low.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could see the pilots even.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was no-- the Poles, they hardly had any anti-aircraft guns.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were shooting with their rifles to try to shoot down the planes with their hand rifles.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What choice did they have?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were running like this for a few hours until we got tired.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we heard that the Germans are approaching from all sides.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So there was no point in running away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They would get us in any case.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So my father decided to go back home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So we came back into our apartment and we-- we settled in and we prepared ourselves for the Germans to come in.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But in the meantime, they shelled the city was heavy guns.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we had to sit in the shelters all the time while they were bombarding.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we already prayed-- we, as children, we were terrified.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We prayed already the Germans should come in because we couldn't take it anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the-- the-- the-- the-- every time the shell came very close, exploded, it was unbearable.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And this went on from Wednesday morning till Friday morning and on Friday morning, I was standing with my brother outside and we could see the German-- the-- the German cars approaching with the German flag and a swastika.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a few cars, they drove up to the main town hall, wasn't very far from us and they went inside.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
